A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 16-11-127 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 carrying weapons or long guns in unauthorized locations, so as to add certain facilities of the
3 Geo. L. Smith II Georgia World Congress Center Authority to the locations in which the
4 carrying of weapons or long guns is prohibited; to provide for related matters; to repeal
5 conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 Code Section 16-11-127 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to carrying
9 weapons or long guns in unauthorized locations, is amended in subsection (b) by striking "or"
10 at the end of paragraph (6), by replacing the period with "; or" at the end of paragraph (7),
11 and by adding a new paragraph to read as follows:
12 "(8) Within facilities of the Geo. L. Smith II Georgia World Congress Center Authority,
13 as described in Code Section 10-9-14.1, which are enclosed by fencing that is at least 8
14 feet in height and includes prominent postings of notice of such restrictions at all access
15 points; provided, however, that such facility is not a location where vehicles are permitted
16 to park."
